  "StockRole": "Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "Nimakachi Fusion was building these when the Word of Blake hit Tematagi and destroyed the plant. Should have been the end of the design but Wakazashi picked up production in the mid-3070s. The Draconis Combine used them exclusively for a while but by the Dark Age mercenaries and pirates were getting their hands on them through whatever channels they could. Nearly 173 kph in bursts with ECM and an Active Probe running is a hard combination to deal with. The weapons are light but that was never the point.",
